## Refresh

Command:
`nix flake update`

Summary:
Passed. Nix updated `flake.lock` input `nixpkgs`:
`github:NixOS/nixpkgs/b5aa0fbd538984f6e3d201be0005b4463d8b09f8?...` dated 2026-06-29
to
`github:NixOS/nixpkgs/65179426c83bb3f6bc14898b42ea1c6f01d374b0?...` dated 2026-07-02.

Command:
`nix develop -c mise latest tuist`

Summary:
Passed. Output included the dev shell banner and reported latest Tuist version `4.201.0`.

Command:
`apply_patch`

Summary:
Updated `.mise.toml` Tuist pin from `4.200.5` to `4.201.0`.

